{"title": "Checking Credentials (Local)", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "smb-protocol/authentication/checking-credentials-local", "html": "<h1 id=\"checking-credentials-local\">Checking credentials (Local)</h1>\n<h3 id=\"userpasswordhashes\">User/Password/Hashes</h3>\n<p>Adding <code>--local-auth</code> to any of the authentication commands with attempt to logon locally.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;USERNAME&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;PASSWORD&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--local-auth\nnxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--local-auth\nnxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;USERNAME&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;LM:NT&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--local-auth\nnxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;USERNAME&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;NTHASH&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--local-auth\nnxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>localguy<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;HASH&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--local-auth\nnxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>localguy<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;HASH&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--local-auth\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Results will display the hostname next to the user:password</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">    </span>SMB<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.101<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>HOSTNAME<span class=\"w\">          </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>HOSTNAME<span class=\"se\">\\U</span>sername:Password<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\">  </span>\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Checking credentials (Local) User/Password/Hashes Adding --local-auth to any of the authentication commands with attempt to logon locally. nxc smb &lt;CIDR&gt; -u &lt;USERNAME&gt; -p &lt;PASSWORD&gt; ", "tags": []}